                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18201206-56-defend576 t18201206-56-punish353"></join>
               Transported for Life
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Bailey.</p>
